body:
# [Visit my full site!](https://bjschafer.com)

***

Hi.  I'm Braxton.  I'm a CS student at Ripon College, minoring in Spanish.  I graduate in August.  Most of my programming is done in Python, C++, and Bash, but I'm also more or less fluent in C, Java, C# (including ASP.NET), MSSQL, Sqlite, and LaTeX.

My pet project right now is [Brewmaster](http://bjschafer.github.io/brewmaster), a tool for managing multiple computers using Homebrew.  Feel free to submit a pull request!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
